'''lecithin'''
{{wikipedia}}

# a [[phospholipid]] found in egg [[yolk]]s, and in all [[plant]]s, especially [[soy]].  It is a major constituent of [[cell]] [[membrane]]s, and is commonly used as a [[food additive]] (as an [[emulsifier]]).
